[IMG]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PixysOS/Pixys_doc/twelve/twelve-stuff/install.png[/IMG]
[B]- Backup your personal data (Important)
- Download latest build
- Boot to recovery (PixysOS recovery recommended).
- Wipe the System, Cache, Data and ART/Dalvik cache.
- Flash the ROM.
- Flash the root solution of your choice (optional).
- Reboot your device.[/B]

